---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RoadmapTool from '../components/RoadmapTool.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Baby Plan | Your Milestone Roadmap">
  <header class="bg-baltic-900 text-white py-20 px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 italic">The Baby Plan</h1>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">The Smartest Way to Navigate Parenthood.</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-baltic-50 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Stop guessing, start planning. Get a personalized, week-by-week roadmap for your pregnancy and your child’s first 10 years.
    </p>
    <RoadmapTool />
  </header>



  <section class="bg-baltic-900 text-white py-24 px-4 border-b border-yale-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-6 border border-yale-500 text-yale-300 rounded-full text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">
      System Status: 2026 Tech Standards Active
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
      Is Your Nursery <span class="text-yale-400">Security-Proof?</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-baltic-200 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      A high-speed, technical roadmap for the modern parent. We audit the gear, secure your network, and plan the first 10 years.
    </p>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded-lg shadow-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Enter email for the 2026 Smart Nursery PDF" class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 text-baltic-900 outline-none rounded-md" />
      <button class="bg-yale-600 hover:bg-yale-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-bold transition-all">
        Download Audit →
      </button>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-baltic-400 font-mono">Join 2,500+ parents on the "Nursery Tech" list.</p>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="py-20 px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-baltic-900 mb-12 flex items-center gap-3">
    <span class="w-8 h-px bg-yale-500"></span> Current Hardware Reviews
  </h2>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="border border-alabaster-200 p-6 rounded-sm bg-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
      <div class="text-xs font-mono text-yale-600 mb-2">NETWORK SECURITY / SLEEP</div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-baltic-900">Nanit Pro: The 2026 Wi-Fi Audit</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">Can your network handle 4K streaming? We test the Nanit Pro against the latest mesh systems.</p>
      <a href="/blog/nanit-review" class="text-baltic-900 font-bold border-b-2 border-yale-400 pb-1 hover:text-yale-600">Read Analysis →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-alabaster-200 p-6 rounded-sm bg-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
      <div class="text-xs font-mono text-yale-600 mb-2">INFRASTRUCTURE / CONNECTIVITY</div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-baltic-900">Best Mesh Wi-Fi for Smart Nurseries</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">Why the Eero 6+ is the "Safety Stack" essential for 2026. Dead zones are a safety risk.</p>
      <a href="/blog/eero-6-plus" class="text-baltic-900 font-bold border-b-2 border-yale-400 pb-1 hover:text-yale-600">Read Analysis →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-alabaster-200 p-6 rounded-sm bg-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
      <div class="text-xs font-mono text-yale-600 mb-2">HARDWARE / DATA</div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-baltic-900">SNOO Smart Sleeper: ROI Analysis</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">The high-ticket investment guide. Is the data tracking worth the $1,600 price tag?</p>
      <a href="/blog/snoo-review" class="text-baltic-900 font-bold border-b-2 border-yale-400 pb-1 hover:text-yale-600">Read Analysis →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



  <section class="py-16 px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="bg-yale-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Build Your Ultimate Amazon Registry</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 opacity-90">Don't waste money on gear you won't use. Get our pre-vetted list of essentials.</p>
      <a href="https://amazon.com" class="inline-block bg-white text-yale-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-baltic-50 transition-colors">
        Start My Amazon Registry
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>




    
    <section class="py-16 px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-alabaster-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="text-yale-500 font-bold mb-2">Stage 1</div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-baltic-900 text-lg">The Blueprint</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Pre-conception to Birth. Prep your body, home, and career for the big arrival.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-alabaster-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="text-yale-500 font-bold mb-2">Stage 2</div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-baltic-900 text-lg">The Arrival</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">0 to 12 Months. Master sleep cycles, feeding logistics, and postpartum recovery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-alabaster-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="text-yale-500 font-bold mb-2">Stage 3</div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-baltic-900 text-lg">The Discovery</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">1 to 4 Years. Navigating milestones, nutrition, and early learning through play.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-alabaster-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="text-yale-500 font-bold mb-2">Stage 4</div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-baltic-900 text-lg">The Legacy</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">5+ Years. Financial planning, school readiness, and long-term family wellness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>


</Layout>